# SISRI Documentation Conventions

## Key Docs
- `README.md` - Quick start, architecture, links
- `docs/Next-Steps-Plan.md` - Roadmap (Fact_Sales fix, Dim_Products conformed)
- `docs/App-Structure-Guide.md` - Code structure
- `docs/Admin-Instruction-Manual.md` - Operations
- `docs/Check-In-Checklist.md` - Pre-commit steps

## When Updating
- Add links to `Next-Steps-Plan.md` when documenting roadmap items
- Update `docs/Documentation-Summary.md` when adding new docs
- Source types: Dimension, Dimension_Conformed, Fact_Sales, Fact_Conformed, System

## Naming
- Use PascalCase for source/table names in docs
- Use backticks for code: `ETL.Staging_Fact_Sales_Conformed`
